Product name: Lariat Lava Diffuser Necklace, Essential Oil Diffuser, Teardrop Lava Bead Necklace, Diffuse Necklace, Aromatherapy Jewelry, Gold
Description:
Gold Circle Infinity Lava Bead Necklace
A genuine black lava rock pendant dangles from a sparkling gold filled chain. This lariat features a 24k gold vermeil infinity hoop, creating an elegant and modern aromatherapy diffuser necklace.
- Genuine lava teardrop pendant measures approx. 14mm
- 24k gold vermeil infinity circle measures 12mm
- Sparkling 14k gold filled cable chain
- Total length of necklace shown in picture is 19 Inches - Make sure to measure and select the right length for you!
- Lariat necklaces are adjustable and can be worn with infinity circle close to the neck or anywhere along the chain
- To ensure your lariat necklace stays in place, loop the dangling section a few times
Each piece is beautifully packaged in our signature aqua jewelry box - perfect for gifting! :)
***Lariat Sizing Instructions***
To ensure a perfect fit, take a piece of string and wrap it around your neck creating a lariat at the length you would like. As lariat necklaces do not have clasps, make sure the string will comfortably fit over your head. Measure your string and select the length (in inches) closest to your measurement from the drop down menu.
*How to infuse your lava rock jewelry with essential oil
Apply 1-2 drops of your favorite essential oil to infuse larger lava rock beads and pendants. For smaller beads, gently rub 1-2 drops of essential oil between fingers and apply.
Lava rock beads are naturally porous, soaking up essential oil and gently diffusing the scent with the help of your body heat. Enjoy 2-5 days of aromatherapy and reapply oil as desired. 
 
Special Note:
Every lava bead is as unique as a fingerprint- the porous nature of genuine lava stones creates patterns of tiny ‘craters’ on each bead. Lava pendants and beads will inevitably vary from the photo in stone shape, crater size, and pattern.
